.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-LOCAL-HTLC-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-local-htlc-count \- FEAT-2042 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-local-htlc-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-local-htlc-count for lightning CLI (FEAT-2042).
.PP
Counts the total number of local (outgoing) HTLCs across all peer channels
by querying listpeerchannels.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
